data.description: Move-in ready 3/2/2 townhome in Lubbock Cooper ISD on a cul-de-sac! Feels new! Open floor plan with light and bright paint throughout! Isolated primary suite with huge walk in shower! Turf in the front for easy upkeep and natural grass in the back yard-kept green with a sprinkler system for easy care! Rear entry 2 car garage! Cozy gas fireplace turns on with a flip of a switch. Open concept living/dining/kitchen makes for an ideal floor plan. Granite countertops in kitchen! Lighting fixtures are absolutely gorgeous! Don't miss the built ins in the lower cabinets. GREAT storage in this home!
